headline: TC Energy Q4 Earnings & Revenues Surpass Estimates, Dividend Raised
summary: TRP anticipates its 2026 comparable EBITDA to be between C$11.6 billion and C$11.8 billion, with net capex to be between C$5.5 billion and C$6 billion.
